{"Id":81791,"Title":"巧言","Dynasty":"先秦","Author":"诗经","Context":"悠悠昊天，曰父母且。无罪无辜，乱如此怃。昊天已威，予慎无罪。昊天大怃，予慎无辜。乱之初生，僭始既涵。乱之又生，君子信谗。君子如怒，乱庶遄沮。君子如祉，乱庶遄已。君子屡盟，乱是用长。君子信盗，乱是用暴。盗言孔甘，乱是用餤。匪其止共，维王之邛。奕奕寝庙，君子作之。秩秩大猷，圣人莫之。他人有心，予忖度之。跃跃毚兔，遇犬获之。荏染柔木，君子树之。往来行言，心焉数之。蛇蛇硕言，出自口矣。巧言如簧，颜之厚矣。彼何人斯，居河之麋。无拳无勇，职为乱阶。既微且尰，尔勇伊何。为犹将多，尔居徒几何。","PoertyType":null,"Cipai":"","Status":1,"Rank":0,"Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"First":null,"Guid":"b3fc22352792207e567733c8e8b15b00","Step":0,"Verses":[{"Id":9643625,"Sentence":"悠悠昊天，曰父母且。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"yōu yōu hào tiān ，yuē fǔ mǔ jū ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":0,"Dynasty":"先秦"},{"Id":9643626,"Sentence":"无罪无辜，乱如此怃。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"mó zuì mó gū ，luàn rú ci wǔ ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":1,"Dynasty":"先秦"},{"Id":9643627,"Sentence":"昊天已威，予慎无罪。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"hào tiān yi wēi ，yú shèn mó zuì ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":2,"Dynasty":"先秦"},{"Id":9643628,"Sentence":"昊天大怃，予慎无辜。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"hào tiān dà wǔ ，yú shèn mó gū ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":3,"Dynasty":"先秦"},{"Id":9643629,"Sentence":"乱之初生，僭始既涵。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"luàn zhī chū shēng ，jiàn shi jì hán ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":4,"Dynasty":"先秦"},{"Id":9643630,"Sentence":"乱之又生，君子信谗。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"luàn zhī yòu shēng ，jūn zi xìn chán ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":5,"Dynasty":"先秦"},{"Id":9643631,"Sentence":"君子如怒，乱庶遄沮。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"jūn zi rú nù ，luàn shù chuán jǔ ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":6,"Dynasty":"先秦"},{"Id":9643632,"Sentence":"君子如祉，乱庶遄已。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"jūn zi rú zhi ，luàn shù chuán yi ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":7,"Dynasty":"先秦"},{"Id":9643633,"Sentence":"君子屡盟，乱是用长。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"jūn zi lǚ méng ，luàn shì yòng cháng ","Tag":null